Setup Steps
Install Exchange Online 

PowerShell Module

Install-Module -Name ExchangeOnlineManagement
Connect to Exchange Online
Connect-ExchangeOnline -UserPrincipalName admin@company.com -ShowProgress $true
Create Shared Mailbox for Centralized Monitoring
New-Mailbox -Shared -Name "UserActivityMonitor" -DisplayName "User Activity Monitor"
Configure Journaling / Forwarding
Forward all user emails to the shared mailbox:
Get-Mailbox -ResultSize Unlimited | ForEach-Object {
    Set-Mailbox $_.UserPrincipalName -DeliverToMailboxAndForward $true -ForwardingSMTPAddress "UserActivityMonitor@company.com"
}
Admin Access
Admin user monitors the shared mailbox in Outlook or via PowerShell:
Search-Mailbox -Identity "UserActivityMonitor@company.com" -SearchQuery 'Received:today' -TargetMailbox "admin@company.com"

ব্যাখ্যা:

সমস্ত user email centralized mailbox-এ forward হবে।
Admin user read-only বা full access নিতে পারবে auditing ও security monitoring-এর জন্য।
Compliance ও security policy অনুসারে ব্যবহার করা যাবে।

